title: Hawkwind 1992 Reading 19th May 1992 320 kbps mp3
description:
An excellent audience recording of this show was has been in circulation for some time.  Unfortunately there were occasional breaks in the recording which always spoiled the fun.

A few years ago a second recording of the show surfaced.  It was also incomplete, but the breaks were in different places, so .........

This torrent comprises a merge of the two recordings, producing a complete, seamless recording (except for the disk flip between Secret Agent and Assassins of Allah).  This complete version has been in circulation since it was produced, so may not be new to everyone, but I thought it important to describe its lineage.
